dct_description_sm: World map showing the three known continents, Asia, Europe and Africa within a circle. Title supplied by cataloger. From: Isidori Iunioris Hispalensis Episcopi Epistola ... [known as the Etymologiae]. [Augsburg] : Per Gintherum Zainer ex Reutlingen progenitum literis impressi ahenis, 1472, 19 die mensis Noue[m]bris.
